Dear Anonymous

Thank you very much for your comments regarding your recent experience in the Radiography Department. I am so pleased you found the service to be fabulous and the staff delivered a first rate service.

I am very sorry that you found the behaviour   from the receptionist to be unacceptable and I would like to look into this matter further. To do this accurately, I would need some more information from you to identify you on our system and would like to ask you to contact the Patient Relations Team directly on 0121 424 0808 at your convenience or email: uhb-tr.Complaints-ConcernsandCompliments@nhs.net 

I look forward to hearing from you and once again thank you for providing your comments, patient feedback and a positive patient experience is extremely important to us.

With kind regards
Patient Experience Team

